headline: After Disappointing in 2025, These Blue-Chip Dividend Stocks Are Way Too Cheap
summary: These five top blue-chip stocks underperformed last year and look poised to rebound in 2026. Two are Warren Buffett holdings in Berkshire Hathaway.
